heading: Выбрать консультанта
subheading: Выберите консультанта, с которым хотите поговорить на видео, аудио или текстовой консультации
modal_coupon_heading: Введите свой купон, чтобы использовать его
coupon_paragraph: Coupons provide “no-cost” sessions and are sponsored by our partners.RU
coupon_paragraph_two: If you received a coupon code from a social media campaign or a partner, please copy and paste that below. After you submit the coupon code, you will see any providers that support it and their availability. A coupon may support one or more sessions. The platform will indicate if the coupon has expired or reached the maximum session usage.RU
